{{Quote|We fought many soldiers during the Mandalorian Wars. The Onderonians were certainly brave&mdash;but they were disorganized and stupid.|[[Mandalore (title)/Legends|Mandalore]] [[Canderous Ordo]]|<ref name="Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords">''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords]]''</ref>}}
[[File:Sbofond.jpg|thumb|right|250px]]
'''Onderon Soldiers''' performed both the functions of [[Onderonian military|army]] and law enforcement on [[Onderon/Legends|Onderon]]. Ranks below commissioned officer wore brown uniforms with a cap and a mask that covered the lower half of their face, with officers wearing a very dark shade of blue-gray. Both classes of uniform were offset with gold piping and topped with a white wrap-like garment covering the shoulders.

